title: RMap Dify Chatbot
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it using the
  metadata from this file.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Philipp
    family-names: Wiesenbach
    email: philipp.wiesenbach@uni-heidelberg.de
    affiliation: Heidelberg University
repository-code: 'https://github.com/dieterich-lab/RmapDifyChatbot'
abstract: >-
  Metadata-aware Dify chatbot for scientific paper retrieval and analysis.
  Includes advanced-chat workflow with iterative retrieval, paper metadata
  extraction using hybrid LLM/regex pipelines, bulk upload tooling for
  Dify knowledge bases, and development utilities for workflow maintenance.
keywords:
  - dify
  - chatbot
  - scientific papers
  - metadata extraction
  - knowledge retrieval
  - llm
  - rag
